I'm going to las vegas.

19
00:03:17,865 --> 00:03:19,495
Where else?

20
00:03:19,500 --> 00:03:22,300
( car doors close )

21
00:03:22,303 --> 00:03:24,603
( engine starts )

22
00:03:24,605 --> 00:03:27,705
( ned albright's "the seventh
son" playing )

23
