1100
01:08:08,718 --> 01:08:10,648
What all came back to you?

1101
01:08:10,654 --> 01:08:12,754
One night about a month ago,

1102
01:08:12,756 --> 01:08:14,316
I just couldn't sleep.

1103
01:08:14,324 --> 01:08:16,424
I don't know why,
but I got in my car,

1104
01:08:16,426 --> 01:08:18,126
