1105
01:09:12,214 --> 01:09:14,824
Lucille:
<i>I got real sad</i>
<i>lookin' at that room,</i>

1106
01:09:14,818 --> 01:09:17,148
<i>All messed up,</i>
<i>just the way we left it.</i>

1107
01:09:18,687 --> 01:09:20,417
<i>I guess I was hoping</i>
<i>you'd be there somehow.</i>

1108
01:09:31,200 --> 01:09:32,870
