1109
01:10:17,479 --> 01:10:20,449
<i>Maybe it was just a dream.</i>
<i>I don't know.</i>

1110
01:10:20,450 --> 01:10:23,820
But that's when it happened,
julian.

1111
01:10:23,820 --> 01:10:25,550
That's when you and me
made this baby

1112
01:10:25,555 --> 01:10:26,985
I have inside of me.

