1115
01:11:14,803 --> 01:11:16,703
It's holding water.

1116
01:11:16,706 --> 01:11:18,406
I wish julian was here.

1117
01:11:20,776 --> 01:11:22,976
I got a funny feeling
about all this.

1118
01:11:25,681 --> 01:11:27,621
