should I expect you?

1206
01:17:16,232 --> 01:17:19,332
Midnight? Ok, sure. Midnight.

1207
01:17:19,335 --> 01:17:21,895
Gimme that damn phone!

1208
01:17:21,904 --> 01:17:25,014
Now, you listen to me,
you cowardly son of a bitch!

1209
01:17:25,008 --> 01:17:26,708
I want my--

1210
