1219
01:17:50,366 --> 01:17:52,296
Well, not me!

1220
01:17:56,204 --> 01:17:58,374
Always sitting!

1221
01:18:01,677 --> 01:18:02,877
Where you going?

1222
01:18:02,879 --> 01:18:04,449
